Do not download the gui installer - rather get the archive 

https://www.enterprisedb.com/download-postgresql-binaries

Unzip the archive in prgs directory
Add the pgsql/bin to the PATH variable

Create tablespace directory for the postgre daemon 
- create a directory under databases/pgsql
- cd to databases/pgsql
$ initdb .


Start the postgres sql daemon by
$ pg_ctl -D . -l logfile start


# create db
createdb universum_db

# login into psql
psql --dbname universum_db

